Pentamedia Portal

is written in python3.

=== Dependencies

  Juno - light webframework (http://github.com/dodo/juno)
  Jinja2 - tmeplate engine (http://jinja.pocoo.org/2/)
  SQLAlchemy - database framework (http://www.sqlalchemy.org/)
  
=== Install

  get setuptools from http://code.google.com/p/python-incompatibility/
  install all denpendies
  use py3k branch from juno
  convert jinja2 with 2to3
  run sa2to3.py in sqlalchemy
  apply patches on your python3 library
  
=== Use

  start server.py  
  
